               <head>Collection of liturgical, philosophical, and halakhical works</head>
               
               
               
               <msContents rend="visible">
                  
                  
                  
                  <summary>A collection of liturgical, philosophical, and halakhical works. </summary>
                  
                  
                  
                  <textLang mainLang="he"/>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="" class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85070315">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="2r" to="9v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Milḥamot ha-Shem</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">מלחמות השם</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en">Zarka, Joseph ben Jehudah</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he">זרקא, יוסף בן יהודה</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>A poem on the contest between Bible and Talmud. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="" class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85070287">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="10r" to="50v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Hilkhot ha-sheḥitah</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">הלכות שחיטה</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The rules are accompanied by a commentary. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="" class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85070287">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="51r" to="58r"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Hilkhot bediḳah</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">הלכות בדיקה</title>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="" class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85106125">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="58v" to="60r"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Perushim ha-tefilot</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">פרושים על התפלות</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Short disqusitions on the liturgical pieces. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="" class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85045109">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="60v" to="64v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Musare ha-pilosofim</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">מוסרי הפילוסופים</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en" key="viaf.org/viaf/19690624">Ḥunayn ibn Isḥaq al-ʻIbadi, 809-873</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he" key="viaf.org/viaf/19690624">חנין בן אסחאק</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>In the Hebrew translation of Judah ben Solomon Harizi. The work begins with the translatior's introduction, folio 60v. The leaves at the end have been left blank, with the exception of part of folio 63r, which contains the opening of Maimonides' Sheloshah ʻasar ʻiḳarim. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
               
               
               
